# Worked example: Traditional academic medical center site (MSKCC) running Pfizer ONCO-423.
# Demonstrates the v0.2.0 Site / StudySite split, the System three-axis pattern
# (Sponsor-operated EDC + Site-operated ISF), the Equipment-System distinction
# (freezer + IoT temp monitor + temperature log), and the full Delegation Log
# (PI + sub-I + coordinator + pharmacist).

