# === System: Site-operated ISF (MSKCC's local Iron Mountain repository) ===
# Pfizer has NO triple linking to this System — Pfizer doesn't see this URL.
# Pfizer accesses MSKCC essential records via monitoring visits (R3 2.3.5),
# not via direct System access.

